Clear 20 Co-op Quests

Take on quests with other players in co-op.
From Events, select an event marked with, and then select Group to join that quest in co-op.
Before embarking on the quest, select Host or Guest.
Joining as the host will deplete your link bell .
Using your link bell will earn you additional link bell rewards after clearing the quest.
Once the other players are ready, begin the quest.
Joining as a guest does not deplete your link bell .
Once you're ready for battle, tap Ready.
The quest can begin once all other players are ready, too.
*You can tap as a guest to also use your link bell for link bell rewards.
After clearing a co-op quest, you'll earn co-op rewards based on the number of players who joined the quest.
